OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy with rain across the
OL,6,Fwest in the morning, this spreading
OL,7,Facross eastern parts in the afternoon.
OL,8,FTurning drier across the west through
OL,9,Fthe afternoon. Mild around Inverness
OL,10,Fand Nairn.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FRain over the east at first,
OL,13,Fclearing through the evening and
OL,14,Fturning wintry over the hills.
OL,15,FOtherwise dry with increasingly clear
OL,16,Fskies, allowing a widespread frost to
OL,17,Fdevelop.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
