OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FDry with good prolonged sunny
OL,6,Fspells, though feeling cooler than
OL,7,Frecent days. Cloudier in the west with
OL,8,Fincreasingly strong south to southwest
OL,9,Fwinds.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FDry
OL,12,Fwith some bright spells in east on
OL,13,FSaturday, windy and cloudier in west
OL,14,Fwith occasional rain. Variable cloud
OL,15,Fand bright spells Sunday and Monday
OL,16,Fwith occasional rain, mostly west.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
